<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      .email-container {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .header {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #555;
      }
      .button {
        display: block;
        width: 200px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 18px;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='email-container'>
      <h1 class='header'>Welcome to Pharmacy!</h1>
      <div class='content'>
        <p>Thanks for signing up! There's just one final step to secure your
          account.</p>
        <p>Please click the button below to verify your email address:</p>
        <a
          href={{verificationUrl}}
          class='button'
          style='color: #ffffff;'
        >Verify Email Address</a>
        <p>This link will expire in 1 hour for your security.</p>
        <p>If you did not sign up for an account with Pharmacy, you can safely
          ignore this email.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>&copy; {{year}} Pharmacy. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>